Properties.Tag: Select [K_AP].[CAP] As [Тип адресной программы], Max([K_AP].[NAP]) As [Наименование АП], [AP_Obj].[CObj] As [Код объекта], Max([AP_Obj].[NObj]) As [Наименование объекта АП], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_UL_Z].[CUL] As [Заказчик], Max([K_UL_Z].[NUL]) As [Наименование заказчика], [DOC].[DU_OT] As [Дата отдела], [AP_Obj].[Y_Begin] As [Год начала], [AP_Obj].[Y_End] As [Год завершения] From ((((((((([AP_Obj] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_AP] With (NoLock) On ([AP_Obj].[K_APID]=[K_AP].[K_APID])) Inner Join [K_DIST] With (NoLock) On ([AP_Obj].[K_DISTID]=[K_DIST].[K_DISTID])) Left Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([AP_Obj].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([AP_Obj].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_Z] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID]=[K_UL_Z].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_R] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID_PARENT]=[K_UL_R].[K_ULID])) Left Join [K_GOBJ] With (NoLock) On ([AP_Obj].[K_GOBJID]=[K_GOBJ].[K_GOBJID])) Left Join [PRB_R_AP_Obj] With (NoLock) On ([AP_Obj].[AP_ObjID]=[PRB_R_AP_Obj].[AP_ObjID])) Left Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([PRB_R_AP_Obj].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Where |0 Group by [K_AP].[CAP], [AP_Obj].[CObj], [DOC].[CDOC], [K_UL_Z].[CUL], [DOC].[DU_OT], [AP_Obj].[Y_Begin], [AP_Obj].[Y_End] Order by |1
